Nice to have commands;

neofetch      - asci display sys info
htop          - system monitor
-k            - kill process
clear
exit
ping 1.1.1.1  - check connection

ifconfig      - for network details



Basics;

cd            - change directory (ex;  cd bash.history) 
ls            - list files
ls -lh        - long way list files
xdg-open      - for openning files (ex; go to file location by cd/ and  xdg-open dead-1648663676344-142.jpg)




sudo apt install spotify   - for installing spotify
